file.name: multipart-form-data-conflicts.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Multipart
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /object/conflicts:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              properties:
                info:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    name:
                      type: string
                    size:
                      type: number
                file:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
            encoding:
              info:
                headers:
                  # The value header should conflict with the value property we automatically create
                  value:
                    schema:
                      type: string
              file:
                headers:
                  # The filename header should conflict with the filename property we automatically create
                  filename:
                    schema:
                      type: string
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
